Do not use this anymore
=======================
This concept has been superseded by generating Apache Karaf as part of ECF's regular build [1].

[1] http://dev.eclipse.org/mhonarc/lists/ecf-dev/msg06391.html


Old instructions
=========================
1.) Install pax-runner from https://ops4j1.jira.com/wiki/display/paxrunner/Pax+Runner
1a.) wget http://search.maven.org/remotecontent?filepath=org/ops4j/pax/runner/pax-runner-assembly/1.8.5/pax-runner-assembly-1.8.5-jdk15.zip -O pax-runner-assembly.zip
1b.) unzip pax-runner-assembly.zip
1c.) dos2unix pax-runner-*/bin/pax-run*.sh # (on unix only)
2.) pax-runner-*/bin/pax-run.sh --args=https://github.com/ECF/ECF4Felix/raw/master/eclipse.ecf.dosgi.args
3.) Open http://localhost:8080/system/console/
